    <p>In Global Navigation, click the <strong>Account</strong> link [1], then click the <strong>Settings</strong> link [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="edit_settings" data-step-uuid="7D8CCB40-E0DC-0138-40B0-12F2183ABDFB">
    <h2 id="edit_settings" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Edit Settings</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/799/822/original/a90d70ad-64a8-4214-b280-a31a1ecc3e9d.png" srcset="" alt="Edit Settings" height="430" width="276">
